            "heading": "",
            "highlight_font": "body",
            "seo_heading": "h2",
            "size": "h2",
            "content": "<p>FabricSG began with a love for handcrafted textiles and a deep respect for the heritage of Indian block printing.<br/><br/>We work with cotton because it feels soft, lives beautifully, and brings comfort into everyday spaces. From table linens and napkins to quilts and pillow covers, each piece is designed to feel timeless, practical and warm.<br/><br/>Our collections are inspired by homes that are layered, lived in and full of personality. We believe the pieces you use every day should feel special without being precious.<br/><br/>Every textile carries the character of handwork, the beauty of imperfect detail, and the story of traditional craftsmanship reimagined for modern living.<br/><br/>Thank you for supporting handmade design and the artisan traditions behind every piece.</p>"
          }
